SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES
Compress Journey History Data Downloads

Because downloads are limited to 1 GB, a compressed 1-GB journey history data file can contain more data than an uncompressed file of the same size.

Where: This change applies to Marketing Cloud Engagement in Corporate and Enterprise editions and to customers with the Journey Builder add-on.

How: Issue a POST request to the /interaction/v1/interactions/journeyhistory/download endpoint. Include the accept-encoding header in your request with a value of gzip or deflate. The API returns the requested data by using the compression method that you specified.
